THIS IS GUI MOD FOR AIRCRACK+REAVER [OPEN SOURCE]
Coded by Cr0n05

INSTALL Debian [ APT-GET ]
apt-get install reaver
apt-get install aircrack-ng
apt-get install perl-tk

INSTALL ArchLinux
pacman -S aircrack-ng
pacman -S perl-tk
go to AUR reaver and install
./configure
make
make install

INSTALL FEDORA
foda-se eu nao uso esta merda mesmo
